{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_team", "channel": "sales_updates", "user": "andrewchang", "message": "Good morning team, just a quick reminder about our sales strategy meeting this afternoon at 2pm. Please come prepared with your updates and ideas.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_team", "channel": "sales_updates", "user": "janedoe", "message": "Thanks for the reminder, Andrew. I've compiled the customer feedback from the past month and will be sharing it in the meeting.", "created_at": 1620501500000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "it_team", "channel": "it_operations", "user": "johndoe", "message": "We've scheduled a system maintenance for this weekend. There should be minimal disruption to our operations, but please save any important work beforehand.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_team", "channel": "sales_updates", "user": "andrewchang", "message": "Great, Jane. Customer feedback is crucial for us to improve our services. Looking forward to your presentation.", "created_at": 1620505000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_team", "channel": "sales_updates", "user": "janedoe", "message": "Andrew, I also have some ideas about how we can improve our in-store customer experience. Can we discuss this in the meeting as well?", "created_at": 1620507000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "it_team", "channel": "it_operations", "user": "andrewchang", "message": "Thanks for the heads up, John. I'll make sure my team is aware of the maintenance schedule.", "created_at": 1620509000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "it_team", "channel": "it_operations", "user": "johndoe", "message": "Team, I was going through our IT operational data post cloud migration. It's really impressive, we've seen a significant reduction in our operational costs.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "it_team", "channel": "it_operations", "user": "johndoe", "message": "To put it in numbers, after investing $3.5 million in the cloud infrastructure migration in 2025, we've managed to reduce our IT operational costs by 24%. This has given us more room to invest in other important areas.", "create_at": 1620500000020}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "it_team", "channel": "it_operations", "user": "andrewchang", "message": "That's great news, John. However, I believe this insight, while valuable for our IT operations, doesn't directly impact our product sales or promotion planning. We need to focus on areas that have been impacted by tariffs for sales analysis.", "create_at": 1620500000040}}
